data.description: Do not miss out on this rare opportunity to live in the desirable community of Beachwalk! This two-story home is positioned against a wooded area and has so much to offer. The spacious main level is perfect for entertaining and conveniently offers a guest bedroom and full bathroom. The gourmet kitchen boasts stainless appliances and large island that overlooks the living and dining room. Owner's suite and jack and jill guest rooms are located on the second floor. Enjoy the wooded views from your screened-in pavered porch. State of the art amenities featuring a 14 acre crystal clear lagoon, restaurants, swim up bar, gym, dog park, and tennis courts.
